Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, I'm going\Nto please you this way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to come,\Njust go ahead, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spray my face whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Keita?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Chiyo. I want to do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, Haruka, it's just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you shouldn't hog Keita's sperm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Let me get some too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. Keita is all of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. Keita is all of ours.\NHow did it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started because of\Nwhat Dad said that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a Mom\NEpisode 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, what is this? It's out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, I've been thinking\Nabout something for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the fact that\Nyou still need a mother!.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sudden, but I've brought\Na couple of candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the daughter at\Na bento shop I often go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not their daughter.\NJust a part-time worker, Jinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Kazuho Tateshina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can become\Nyour mother, but please look after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this young lady is\Na secretary at my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chiyo Sawagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is an excellent young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:03:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I don't know if I'll be of\Nany help, but please look after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? Greet her properly!.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Keita. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean by "mother\Ncandidates"? And why are there two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, it's not two.\NThere's another one coming later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A young detective,\NNoriko Kasukabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking why there are that many!.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, aren't they candidates to be your\Nwife, not my mother? You choose one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so hardheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the person who'll become\Nyour mother, so you have to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these three will be\Nliving with us starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. You'll be choosing one\Nby the end of summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, she'll be your wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's time for me\Nto return to work, Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to all I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I won't be back for a while.\NI'm going on a business trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So apparently...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the last of your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I feel bad that you\Nhad to carry most of it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now, so could\Nyou check up on Miss Sawagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\NOh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's was a pretty loud sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri, are\Nyou okay? I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri,\Nyou're not hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that was embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine. I just fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's because\NI heard a loud thump...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than that though,\Nthat's a lot of stuffed animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, this is... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't resist these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just different\Nfrom my image of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go to bed at night without\Nthem, so that's why I brought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't be.\NBut I'm glad you're not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she okay?\NSeems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to start\Ngetting dinner ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't force yourself to, Kazuho.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Miss Sawagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Miss Sawagiri...\NUm, Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you call me\Nby my first name too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just seems a little too formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:06:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, It just feels kind of rude if I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, could you go pick up\Nsomething from the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is Dad up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wrap my head around\Nthe idea of a mom at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, they're so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I can't think of them as a mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing\Nhere dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming back from practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you riding\Na bike dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school shower is broken,\Nand I'm covered in sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hurry home and shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you standing\Nin this heat with a blank look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An errand for your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, for a mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering if\NI still look that much like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're\Ngoing crazy from this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The break just started.\NDon't go losing it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off. Gonna take a shower ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling me to decide by the end of\Nthe break... It's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,\Nwho's the last person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering if\NI still look that much like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita... Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We're not kids anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long was it\Nsince I had homemade food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kazuho becomes the mom,\NI can eat that kind of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, getting to see her in that apron\Nevery day isn't a bad thing either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, it's not a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alley-oop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What," my foot. Why are\Nyou coming into my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:10:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good evening,\NI'm Noriko Kasukabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me "Mom."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the other candidate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you\Ncoming in from the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's burglars who\Ncome in from windows, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's your mom.\NYou can fawn on me all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mom"? Man, you reek of booze!\NWhat are you, totally drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on, let's try to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're young. So sensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a family\Nresemblance. Just like your dad's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter! Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Let's get along more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alley-oop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Keita, you lick mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, do it with your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to see my boobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, boobs. Is it your\Nfirst time seeing some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breast-feed though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it nice and soft?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Noriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noriko! Noriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, it's time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep sleeping\Njust because it's summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning,\NMiss Sawagiri. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, Noriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't... I didn't do it with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... Man, I did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was following someone last night,\Nand I drank too much at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was out of it on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Keita.\NWe almost went all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit late,\Nbut please look after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With becoming your mom and all,\Nbut it seems we're closer already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, best regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo, best regards too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko, what are you saying?\NDoing such a thing with Jinta's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Oh my! What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the third candidate,\NNoriko Kasukabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Keita too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was kind of like "skinship."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-With that said, let's all get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Few Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be going. I'll be home late, so\Nplease don't wait up and just go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day.
